			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">EXPLORATION CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move character:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad or Left Analog Stick</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Action:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Run:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Zoom in:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Calls up field command screen:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Rotate camera left or right:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 or R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Toggle compass direction (dungeons only):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L2 or R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Open / Close townscope:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Camera control:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Right Analog Stick</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game / Displays in game options menu:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">COMBAT CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move cursor:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad or Left Analog Stick</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Enter command:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Toggle tactics play fair command:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Look command:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Cancel tactics:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Hold to switch HP to SP display:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 or R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Hold to switch from HP to MP display:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L2 or R2 Button</font><br><br>
        &nbsp;</td>
	 </tr>
